    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Complex PCF change adding new BulkActionBar component + 6 bulk actions (Email/Download/Pin/Delete/Doc Type/Share); calls BFF bulk-download endpoint; optimistic UI with Undo; ADR-021 + ADR-022 + ADR-028 binding</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>shared file SemanticSearchControl.tsx with other Phase 4 tasks (040-044, 046)</parallel-reason>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Per spec FR-DOC-02, add a sticky bulk-action bar above the list-view column-header row, visible when ≥1 row is checked. Bar shows: count badge ("N selected"), Clear affordance, and 6 actions: **Email selected** (SPE files as attachments; multi-doc = single email with zip attachment), **Download selected** (calls new BFF endpoint `POST /api/documents/bulk-download` from task 051; multi-doc = single zip), **Pin selected** (localStorage; no Dataverse write), **Delete selected** (soft-delete via Xrm.WebApi; confirmation `Dialog`), **Document Type → selected** (sub-menu of `sprk_documenttype` option values; optimistic UI + 5s Undo toast on success; error toast with Retry on failure), **Share link** (email composer with body containing clickable `sprk_document` record URLs format `https://{env}.crm.dynamics.com/main.aspx?etn=sprk_document&id={guid}&pagetype=entityrecord`, NOT SPE files). Bar appears at ≥1 selection, hides at 0; each action operates on the selected set; failure modes degrade gracefully (toast + Retry).
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Senior frontend developer expert in Fluent UI v9 `Toolbar` + `MessageBar` + `Toast` patterns, optimistic UI with Undo, Xrm.WebApi calls from PCFs, and BFF `authenticatedFetch` via `@spaarke/auth`. Familiar with the existing Semantic Search PCF email pipeline.
  </role>

  <goal>
    NEW `BulkActionBar.tsx` component encapsulating the sticky bar + 6 actions. `SemanticSearchControl.tsx` mounts the bar when `selection.size &gt;= 1`. Download path calls `POST /api/documents/bulk-download` via `authenticatedFetch`, downloads the returned zip stream as a browser file. Doc Type update uses optimistic UI with 5s Undo toast (Fluent v9 `Toast` with action). Delete shows confirmation `Dialog` before Xrm.WebApi soft-delete. PCF builds clean. Code-review + adr-check pass.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      FR-DOC-02 introduces bulk operations after FR-DOC-04 (task 041) gave us multi-select state. The bulk-action bar lives ABOVE the list view column-header row, sticky on scroll. The Download action depends on FR-BFF-02 (task 051) shipping the `POST /api/documents/bulk-download` endpoint. The Doc Type action uses optimistic UI per Owner Clarifications row 12 (apply immediately, 5s Undo). Share link uses Dataverse record URLs (NOT SPE files) per Owner Clarifications row 13. Pin selected writes to the same localStorage key established in task 041 (`spaarke.docs.pinned.{userId}.{matterId}`).
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
